  <h3>Offset and push/pull classes</h3>
  <p>You can introduce offsets or manipulate column ordering at various breakpoints using the following classes, <code>.col-mq-offset-n</code>,<code>.col-mq-push-n</code> and <code>.col-mq-pull-n</code>. This is useful for ensuring HTML is written in a content driven, accessible & mobile first order but be easily visually manipulated.</p>

  <div class="styleguide-example">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 bg--c">.col-md-4</div>
        <div class="col-md-3 bg--d">.col-md-3</div>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-1 bg--e">.col-md-4 .col-md-offset-1</div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-5 col-lg-push-7 bg--d">.col-md-3</div>
        <div class="col-md-7 col-lg-pull-5 bg--f">.col-md-6</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="styleguide-example-code">
    <code><pre>&lt;div class=&quot;container&quot;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;col-md-4 bg--c&quot;&gt;.col-md-4&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;col-md-3 bg--d&quot;&gt;.col-md-3&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;col-md-4 col-md-offset-1 bg--e&quot;&gt;.col-md-4 .col-md-offset-1&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;col-md-5 col-lg-push-7 bg--d&quot;&gt;.col-md-3&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;col-md-7 col-lg-pull-5 bg--f&quot;&gt;.col-md-6&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</pre></code>
  </div>

  <h3>Nesting</h3>
  <p>You can subdivide the grid by nesting. To do this, place a new <code>.row</code> inside of an existing <code>.col-mq-n</code>. You can now subdivide into 12 sub-columns using the <code>.col-mq-n</code> classes.</p>

  <div class="styleguide-example">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6 bg--c">
          .col-md-6
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 bg--d">.col-md-4</div>
            <div class="col-md-8 bg--e">.col-md-8</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 bg--f">.col-md-6</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="styleguide-example-code">
    <code><pre>&lt;div class=&quot;container&quot;&gt;
  &lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;col-md-6 bg--c&quot;&gt;
      .col-md-6
      &lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;col-md-4 bg--d&quot;&gt;.col-md-4&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class=&quot;col-md-8 bg--e&quot;&gt;.col-md-8&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;col-md-6 bg--f&quot;&gt;.col-md-6&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</pre></code>
